-- `Stay Away From Soft Commodities' on Regulation, Prices, SocGen Advises
-- B y   S t u a r t   W a l l a c e
-- 2010-09-21T09:51:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/-stay-away-from-soft-commodities-on-regulation-prices-socgen-advises.html
Investors should “stay away from
soft commodities” after a jump in prices, “expensive”
valuations and the risk of regulation, Societe Generale said in
a report.  “The probability for stricter regulation is increasing
after the impressive spike in soft commodity prices over the
summer,” the bank said in a cross-asset research report dated
yesterday. The recommendation was one of seven Key Calls made by
the strategists. 